{
  "chapter": "108",
  "title": "韩长孺列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "出身与为梁将",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩安国</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成安</span>人，后来迁居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">睢阳</span>。曾向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">驺田生</span>学习<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">韩子</span>、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">杂家</span>的学说。侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中大夫</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>乱时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张羽</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>，抵御<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军于东部边境。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张羽</span>勇力<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>斗，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>持重防守，因此<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军不能越过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之乱被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>平定后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张羽</span>的名声因此显扬。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "为梁使说太后",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母弟</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>宠爱他，允许他自己选置<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>和<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">二千石</span>官，出入游戏，僭拟<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>礼制。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>听说后心中不快。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>知道<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>不高兴，就迁怒于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国使者，不肯接见，追究梁王所作所为。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩安国</span>作为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国使者，拜见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大长公主</span>哭诉道:\"为什么<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>作为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人子</span>的孝道、作为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>的忠心，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>却不体察呢？当日<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">七国</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>叛时，函谷关以东都<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">合从</span>向西进攻，只有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国因最亲而处境最艰难。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>念及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>在关中，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>作乱，一谈起就泪流数行，跪送<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六人</span>，领兵<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>退<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，因此<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵不敢西进，最终<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>亡，都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>的功劳啊。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>以小节苛礼责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>兄都是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝王</span>，所见过的仪制庄重，所以出行时清道警跸，入宫言称警戒，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旗</span>都是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>所赐给他的，就是想向偏远郡县夸耀，在国中驰骋，以向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>夸示，让<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>都知道<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>宠爱他。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国使者来，却要被追究。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>惶恐，日夜涕泣思慕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>，不知所措。为什么<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>作为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>这般孝，作为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>这般忠，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>却不体恤呢？\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大长公主</span>把这些话都告诉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>喜说:\"替我告诉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>。\" 告诉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>后，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>心中的结才解开，就脱下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">冠</span>向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>谢罪说:\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span>之间不能相互教诲，竟给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>添了忧烦。\" 便全部接见了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国使者，厚加赏赐。此后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">梁王（梁孝王）</span>和朝廷更加亲厚欢悦。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>又赐给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>价值<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀金</span>的礼物。他的名声由此显扬，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>廷结交。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "死灰复然",
      "text": "后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">坐法</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">抵</span>罪，蒙<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">狱吏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田甲</span>羞辱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>说:\"死灰难道就不会复燃吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田甲</span>说:\"燃了我就撒尿浇灭它。\" 不久之后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>出缺，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝派使者<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁内史</span>，从囚徒中起用，官至<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">二千石</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田甲</span>逃走了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>说:\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田甲\">甲（田甲）</span>如果不来就任，我就要<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灭</span>了他的宗族。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田甲\">甲（田甲）</span>只得袒肉谢罪。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>笑着说:\"可以浇尿了！你们这种人值得我处置吗？\" 最终善待了他。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "武安请内史",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>的空缺，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>新近得到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙诡</span>，喜欢他，想请求让他做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>听说后，就下诏命梁王让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "说孝王出诡胜",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙诡</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羊胜</span>劝说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>谋求做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>以及增加封地的事，怕<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>廷<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>不同意，就暗中派人<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">刺</span>杀<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>廷当权的谋<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>。还<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>害了前<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>终于听闻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙诡\">诡（公孙诡）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：羊胜\">胜（羊胜）</span>等人的计划，就派使者去<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">捕</span>拿<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙诡\">诡（公孙诡）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：羊胜\">胜（羊胜）</span>，必须抓到。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝使者<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十</span>批到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>以下全国大索，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一个多月（时长）</span>也没抓到。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>得知<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙诡\">诡（公孙诡）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：羊胜\">胜（羊胜）</span>藏在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>那里，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>入见梁王哭诉说:\"主人受辱<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>下当死。大王没有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">良臣</span>，所以事情纷乱至此。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙诡\">诡（公孙诡）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：羊胜\">胜（羊胜）</span>抓不到，请允许<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>辞别赐死。\" 梁王说:\"何至于如此？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>泪流数行，说:\"大王自己估量，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>的关系，比起<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太上皇</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高皇帝</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">临江王</span>的亲密，哪个更亲？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>说:\"比不上。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>说:\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太上皇</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">临江王</span>都是亲<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父子</span>之间，然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高帝\">高帝（汉高帝）</span>说'我提<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三</span>尺<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span>得了<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>'，所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太上皇</span>终究不能过问政事，只居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">栎阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">临江王</span>，是嫡长<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，只因一句话的过失，就被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">废</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临江</span>王；又因宫墙侵占之事，终于在<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>府<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>自。为什么？治理<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>终究不能因私情乱了公义。俗话说:'即使是亲<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>，怎知他不变成<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>？即使是亲<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>，怎知他不变成<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狼</span>？'如今大王身为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之一，听信一邪<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的浮夸之说，触犯皇上禁令，扰乱明法。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>因<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>的缘故，不忍对大王执法。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>日夜涕泣，希望大王自行改悔，而大王始终不醒悟。假如有朝一日<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>宫<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>突然驾崩，大王还能攀附谁呢？\" 话还没说完，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>就泪流数行，向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>谢罪说:\"我现在就交出<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙诡\">诡（公孙诡）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：羊胜\">胜（羊胜）</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙诡\">诡（公孙诡）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：羊胜\">胜（羊胜）</span>自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>使者回朝禀报，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国的事都得以化解，这都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>的力量。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>更加看重<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁共王\">共王（梁共王）</span>即位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">坐法</span>失官，居于家中。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "田蚡荐为北地都尉与大司农",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：年号\">建元（年号）</span>年间，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">武安侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田蚡</span>做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>，亲贵用事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>用价值<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百金</span>的财物送给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田蚡\">蚡（田蚡）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田蚡\">蚡（田蚡）</span>向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>推荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>也素闻他贤能，便召他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">北地都尉</span>，升迁为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大司农</span>。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">闽越</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">东越</span>互相<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span>打，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恢</span>领兵前往。还没到<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>地，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>了他们的王<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">降</span>服，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵也就罢归。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">建元六年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">武安侯</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "议和亲匈奴",
      "text": "<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>前来请求<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">和亲</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>下令让群臣讨论。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恢</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>地人，多次做过边吏，熟悉匈奴之事。他议论说:\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">和亲</span>，大都不过<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>就会又违背盟约。不如不答应，兴兵<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>伐他们。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>说:\"出兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>之外去<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>斗，军队得不到利益。如今<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>凭借战<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>的快捷，心怀禽兽之性，迁徙如<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟</span>飞，难以控制。得其地不足以扩广国土，有其众不足以增强国力，自古以来他们就不被视为中国之人。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军远征<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千里</span>争利，人<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>都会疲惫，匈奴就会以全力制我之弊。况且强<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弩</span>射到极远处，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矢</span>已穿不透<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国的薄<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">缟</span>；冲风的末势，力已吹不起<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸿毛</span>。并非开始时不强劲，而是到末端力衰了。<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>讨不利，不如<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">和亲</span>。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>议论中多附和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>，于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>同意<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">和亲</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "马邑之谋",
      "text": "第二年，也就是<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元光元年</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雁门</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>的豪强<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">聂翁壹</span>通过<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恢</span>向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>进言:\"<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>刚<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">和亲</span>，亲近信任边境，可以用利引诱。\" 暗中派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">聂翁壹</span>做间谍，逃入<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>说:\"我能<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>县令和县丞的吏，献城<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">降</span>，财物可以尽得。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>宠爱信任他，以为可信，应允了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">聂翁壹</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">聂翁壹</span>返回后，诈<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死罪</span>囚，把头挂在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>城上，向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>显示为信物。 说:\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长吏</span>已死，可急速前来。\" 于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>穿越边塞率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀万骑</span>，进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武州塞</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "埋伏设谋",
      "text": "当时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝埋伏<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>骑、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">材官</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十馀万</span>兵，藏于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>旁的山谷中。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骁骑将军</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太仆</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙贺</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">轻车将军</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恢</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将屯将军</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太中大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李息</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">材官将军</span>。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩安国</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军将军</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>都归属<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军</span>。 约定等<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵即刻出击。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恢</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李息</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>另从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>出发主<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>匈奴的辎重。 于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长城</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武州塞</span>。 离<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>还有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀里</span>，沿途<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">掠</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">卤</span>，只见畜牧于野，不见<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>奇怪，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span>打烽燧台，捕获了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武州</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉史</span>。 想<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">刺</span>问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉史</span>。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉史</span>说:\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十万</span>埋伏在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>下。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>回头对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">左右</span>说:\"差点被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝骗了！\" 就引兵退回。 出塞后，说:\"我得到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉史</span>，这是天意。\" 封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉史</span>为\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">天王</span>\"。 边塞上传言<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>已经引兵退去。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵追到边塞，估计追不上，就罢兵。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恢</span>等的兵有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万</span>，听说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>没与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>主力接战，估计去<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>匈奴辎重，必然要与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>精兵<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵势必<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span>，就便宜行事罢兵，都没有立功。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "王恢自杀",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>发怒<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恢</span>不出<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>的辎重，擅自引兵罢归。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王恢\">恢（王恢）</span>说:\"起初约定敌虏进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>城，汉军与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>接战，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>再<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>他的辎重，可以得利。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>得到消息，没到就退回，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万人</span>抵不过敌众，只会<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span>辱罢了。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>固然知道回来会被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩</span>，但这样保全了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万人</span>。\" 于是把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王恢\">恢（王恢）</span>交给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>判<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王恢\">恢（王恢）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">逗桡</span>之罪，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当斩</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王恢\">恢（王恢）</span>私下拿<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千金</span>贿赂<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田蚡\">蚡（田蚡）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田蚡\">蚡（田蚡）</span>不敢向皇上讲情，却对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>说:\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恢</span>首倡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>之事，如今事情没成就<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王恢\">恢（王恢）</span>，这是为<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>报仇。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>朝见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>把<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>的话告诉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>说:\"首先提议<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>之事的，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王恢\">恢（王恢）</span>，因此征发<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十万</span>，听他的话做此事。且纵然没抓到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王恢\">恢（王恢）</span>所部<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>匈奴辎重，也还能有些收获，以慰<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士大夫</span>之心。如今不<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王恢\">恢（王恢）</span>，无法向<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>人交代。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王恢\">恢（王恢）</span>听说后，就自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>了。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "为人与推举",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>为人多大略，智谋足以应合世事，而出于忠厚。他贪嗜财物。但所推举的都是廉洁的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，都是比他贤能的。在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国推举<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">壶遂</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧固</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郅他</span>，都是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>名<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人也因此称赞仰慕他，唯有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>把他视为国家栋梁之才。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>多，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田蚡</span>死，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>代理<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>事务，为皇上导引车驾时堕<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>跛足。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>商议任命丞相，想用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>，派使者探视他，发现他跛得厉害，就改任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平棘侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薛泽</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>病免<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数月（时长）</span>，跛痊愈，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>又任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，调任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫尉</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "屯渔阳失利",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">车骑将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫青</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上谷</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>胡于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">茏城</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>被<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>擒获，后又逃脱；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙敖</span>大量损失士卒:都<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当斩</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">赎为</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：次年\">明年（次年）</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>大举入侵边境，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">辽西太守</span>，又进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雁门</span>，所<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">略</span>达<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">车骑将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫青</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>他们，出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雁门</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">材官将军</span>，屯驻在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渔阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">捕</span>得活俘虏，称<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>已远去。便上书说现在正是田间耕作季节，请求暂时罢除军屯。罢除军屯<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一个多月（时长）</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>大举入侵<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上谷</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渔阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>壁垒中只有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七百馀人</span>，出城与匈奴<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>，不能取胜，又退回壁垒。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">虏</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">略</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀人</span>和牲畜财产而去。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>听说后大怒，派使者责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>。把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>调往更东边，屯驻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">右北平</span>。当时<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>俘虏说匈奴要从东方入侵。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "病欧血死",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>起初做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军</span>，后来逐渐被疏远，下降官位；而新近得宠的壮年<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫青</span>等有功，日益显贵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>既被疏远，默默不得志；将兵屯驻又被<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>欺凌，损失很多，甚为自愧。希望罢归，却被更往东迁徙屯驻，心中郁郁不乐。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数月（时长）</span>，病呕血而死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元朔二年</span>中去世。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">壶遂</span>一同制定<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">律历</span>，亲见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩长孺</span>的义气和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">壶遂</span>的深沉中正、宽厚蕴藉。世人说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>地多<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>，不虚啊！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">壶遂</span>官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">詹事</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>正倚重他准备任命为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，恰逢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：壶遂\">遂（壶遂）</span>去世。不然，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">壶遂</span>内心廉洁、品行修饬，是鞠躬尽瘁的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安国\">安国（韩安国）</span>忠厚，起初担任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国将领。 因事<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">坐法</span>获罪，从囚徒中起用为相。 死灰复燃的际遇，活虏失防的败绩。 推举贤良受人敬重，收受贿金招致讥谤。 流泪规劝使梁王醒悟，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子的节操值得明鉴。"
    }
  }
}